{"tid":1394783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］有姐姐堅持請我食餅","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:36:46.000Z","uid":2038,"like":103,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5d822bb142ec03b3e5caab2edd5476775950506d","tid":1394783,"uid":2038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"頭先參加完快閃任務，戴住頭盔搭地鐵。<br />\n呢個時候，有個姐姐走咗過嚟<br />\n姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請你食丫，食甜嘢個人會開心啲～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗啦，我有返工的 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（黑人問題？）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（其實諗住講我唔係冇飯開、飢餓嘅小朋友）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食多啲甜嘢真係會開心啲呢<br />\n<br />\n然後多謝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/as7FbHC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fas7FbHC.png&h=77c97ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間姐姐仲拎住袋糖問要唔要試埋其他呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係滾動到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n靚女姐姐，雖然個post應該好快沉，或者你冇追開連登。我想講好多謝你呀！原諒我頭先講野1999<br />\n本來一個人戴住頭盔係有少少淆底，唔知會唔會畀廢老挑機公審。原來真係有人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好人一世平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後繼續推爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vy8MRNc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVy8MRNc.png&h=30a7772b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vqo5nTZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqo5nTZ.png&h=b705467c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05c178795dca9a9bfd0ff9d31f08d522b944a800","tid":1394783,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"懇請各大公司容許員工8月5號Home Office/ 彈性上班<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"877b62e5a16c9ed3cf8ded6d1e67bb3919545e5d","tid":1394783,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0efaa243d1e8d688ef0cf2b41127a5b1014ab144","tid":1394783,"uid":30836,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"睇錯做<br />\n［突發］有姐姐堅持請我食<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">波</span></strong>餅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276faad169e777af78f49a551b6d5cdf0670b1ef","tid":1394783,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0efaa243d1e8d688ef0cf2b41127a5b1014ab144","tid":1394783,"uid":30836,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"睇錯做<br />\n［突發］有姐姐堅持請我食<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">波</span></strong>餅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正呀"},{"